    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.36.1"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">1</fw>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">THE WHITE HOUSE 
                        <lb/>
                    WASHINGTON</hi>
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>January 3, 1972</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>On your ninety-first birthday, fans across the nation will be joining your friends and fellow Nebraskans in special congratulations to you and in tribute to the life's work that has so enriched American literature and life.</p>
                
                <p>May the year ahead bring you every happiness and the deep satisfaction of knowing that so many many citizens appreciate and applaud you.</p> 
                <closer>
                    <salute>Sincerely,</salute>
                
                    <signed>Richard Nixon</signed>
                    
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine> 
                        <addrLine>5835 Vine Street</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Lincoln, Nebraska 68508</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
